<h2><a href="http://www.lunatics.tv">Anansi Spaceworks</h2>
<hr>
<p>If you represent an organization and would like to add its name to this page, please contact <a href="mailto:info@defectivebydesign.org">info@defectivebydesign.org</a> with your organization name and URL. In addition to this petition, we are preparing a separate sign-on letter for organizations with the same message. If your organization is interested in signing on to the letter, please let us know in your email.</p>
<p>--><p><em>Please share the Hollyweb image, which is copyright Free Software Foundation 2013, under the <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 Unported license</a>.</em></p>
</div></div></div>  </div>

    </article>
